This directory contains the angular/html5/js-client and goovlet-servlet combo to test the ctools-mobile sample application for the Hackathon

To start the server:

groovy jettystarter.groovy &

to run the app:

localhost:9090/index.html

to test a script

localhost:9090/somescript.groovy

Note: 
 scripts go into webapp/scripts
 static resources (html, js, etc) go into webapp/static
 also see views, controllers, model subdirs in webapp/static 

